dev-clean-metadata.name: doctrine/orm
dev-clean-metadata.description: PHP object relational mapper (ORM) that sits on top of a powerful database abstraction layer (DBAL). One of its key features is the option to write database queries in a proprietary object oriented SQL dialect called Doctrine Query Language (DQL). This provides developers with a powerful alternative to SQL that maintains flexibility without requiring unnecessary code duplication.
